org.apache.poi.sl.draw

Interface DrawFontManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DrawFontManagerDefault 

    public interface DrawFontManager
    Manages fonts when rendering slides. Use this class to handle unknown / missing fonts or to substitute fonts(渲染幻灯片时管理字体。使用此类处理未知/缺失的字体或替换字体)

      • mapFontCharset

        java.lang.String mapFontCharset(java.awt.Graphics2D graphics,
                                FontInfo fontInfo,
                                java.lang.String text)
        Map text charset depending on font family.

        Currently this only maps for wingdings and symbol font (into unicode private use area)

        Depending if the requested font is installed in the system, tbe mapped string varies:
        If the font is registered into the graphics environment the characters are mapped to the private use area. If the font is missing (and hence a AWT logical font is used), the characters are mapped to the corresponding unicode characters

        (根据字体系列映射文本字符集。目前，这仅映射翼形和符号字体（到unicode专用区域中）具体取决于系统中是否安装了请求的字体，映射的字符串会有所不同：如果字体注册到图形环境中，则字符将映射到专用区域。如果缺少字体（因此使用AWT逻辑字体），则字符将映射到相应的unicode字符)
        Parameters:
        graphics - the graphics context to request additional rendering hints(graphics -请求额外渲染提示的图形上下文)
        fontInfo - the font info object corresponding to the text run font(fontInfo -与文本运行字体对应的字体信息对象)
        text - the raw text(文本-原始文本)
        Returns:
        String with mapped codepoints(具有映射码点的字符串)
        See Also:
        Drawing exotic fonts in a java applet, StringUtil.mapMsCodepointString(String)

      • createAWTFont

        java.awt.Font createAWTFont(java.awt.Graphics2D graphics,
                            FontInfo fontInfo,
                            double size,

        Create an AWT font object with the given attributes(使用给定属性创建AWT字体对象)
        Parameters:
        graphics - the graphics context to request additional rendering hints(graphics -请求额外渲染提示的图形上下文)

        size - the font size in points(大小-字体大小（单位：点）)
        bold - true if the font is bold(粗体-如果字体是粗体，则为真)
        italic - true if the font is italic(italic -如果字体是italic，则为真)
        Returns:
        the AWT font object(AWT字体对象)
